OL,3,CQueen 'full of admiration' for group's
OL,4,Ccampaign to save village pub
OL,6,FThe Queen has said she is "full of
OL,7,Fadmiration" for a group's campaign to
OL,8,Fsave their East Sussex village pub,
OL,9,Fthe campaigners have said.
OL,11,FBar operator Punch Pubs put The
OL,12,FFountain Inn in Plumpton Green up for
OL,13,Fsale earlier this year.
OL,15,FVillagers have rallied to raise funds
OL,16,Fto buy the pub, which they said has
OL,17,Fbeen the "heart of the community" for
OL,18,F175 years.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@KO]yD@JOUyD@aO]
