OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781711308
OL,3,CQueen 'full of admiration' for group's
OL,4,Ccampaign to save village pub
OL,6,FThey set up the Fountain Inn Community
OL,7,FBenefit Society to campaign and raise
OL,8,Fmoney and said they have now received
OL,9,Froyal approval.
OL,11,FThe group said the Queen sent a letter
OL,12,Fto a local resident, who told her
OL,13,Fabout the project, writing: "I am full
OL,14,Fof admiration for your efforts to buy
OL,15,Fthe Fountain Inn.
OL,17,F"Please do let me know how you get on."
OL,19,FCamilla's family lived for many years
OL,20,Fin The Laines, a large home on the
OL,21,Fedge of neighbouring village, Plumpton.
OL,26,@uD@]OUyD@AOUyD@gO]
