OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781711308
OL,3,CQueen 'full of admiration' for group's
OL,4,Ccampaign to save village pub
OL,6,FIt comes as the Fountain Inn Community
OL,7,FBenefit Society announced it has
OL,8,Falmost #300,000 in pledges to buy the
OL,9,Fpub, which is listed for sale for
OL,10,F#475,000 plus VAT.
OL,12,FStuart Wallis, chairman of The
OL,13,FFountain Inn Community Benefit
OL,14,FSociety, said on Monday: "Queen
OL,15,FCamilla's backing is a sign of just
OL,16,Fwhat the Fountain Inn means to a
OL,17,Fvillage like Plumpton.
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
