FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781711308
OL,3,CQueen 'full of admiration' for group's
OL,4,Ccampaign to save village pub
OL,6,F"Current and former residents, such as
OL,7,FHer Royal Highness, understand that
OL,8,Fthe pub is and will always be the real
OL,9,Fheart of the community that offers
OL,10,Fsocial engagement across all
OL,11,Fdemographics.
OL,13,F"We are delighted to have had such
OL,14,Fhigh backing in this bid."
OL,16,FThe group of volunteers hope to
OL,17,Fpurchase the pub to then let it to a
OL,18,Ftenant landlord.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@ZO]
